<plot>Shimi is a tax man, but not your usual reposessor. He's not tough or macho, but a loner. He's also a peeping tom, and that's why he likes his job. But when he finds out his female neighbour is betrayed by her husband, he sets out to intervene for the first time in his life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?586333</url></doc>
